Hmm.

13:30.076 --> 13:33.945
So...Sharon and I's wedding
is in June,

13:33.947 --> 13:38.917
And we would really love it
if you and bow would come.

13:38.919 --> 13:42.821
This does not conflict
with the nba finals, does it?

13:42.823 --> 13:44.122
