Yeah, it's you.

14:01.842 --> 14:04.209
You guys don't get it?
All right, everyone, I'd like
to propose a toast.

14:04.211 --> 14:07.345
All right, it feels good to have
everyone here for mother's day,

14:07.347 --> 14:10.114
But today isn't just
about mothers.

14:10.116 --> 14:11.583
It's also about sisters.

14:11.585 --> 14:13.284
Since when?

14:13.286 --> 14:15.854
Rhonda, I feel like I've missed
out on so much of your life

14:15.856 --> 14:18.890
