Okay, okay.

14:58.031 --> 15:00.999
Come on, mom. We all know that
that's not gonna happen.

15:01.001 --> 15:03.601
Rhonda and sharon are in love.
Okay.

15:03.603 --> 15:05.236
[ clink ]
and they're getting married!

15:05.238 --> 15:07.171
Mnh-mnh.
[ laughs ] drink up!

15:07.173 --> 15:09.941
