What?

15:09.943 --> 15:11.175
Mnh-mnh.
Mama.

15:11.177 --> 15:13.311
Mnh-mnh!
What's happening?

15:13.313 --> 15:14.445
Mnh-mnh!
Congratulations.

15:14.447 --> 15:16.080
Unh-unh, not my family.

15:16.082 --> 15:17.448
Not in my family!
Please.
Mama, no, listen. Please.

15:17.450 --> 15:18.449
Please listen.
Not gay, not gay,

15:18.451 --> 15:20.184
Not my baby.
Mama, mama...

15:20.186 --> 15:21.352
Mama! Mama!
No!

15:21.354 --> 15:22.687
Oh, god.
It's not about that.

15:22.689 --> 15:25.256
Black jesus!
Black jesus, help me!

15:25.258 --> 15:26.658
[ wailing ]
what the hell do you think
you're doing?

15:26.660 --> 15:27.992
I -- rhonda, I...

15:27.994 --> 15:31.162
Aah!
No! Oh!

15:31.164 --> 15:34.032
Sharon...
It was a nice brunch.
[ whispers ] happy mother's day.

15:34.034 --> 15:38.436
[ ruby sobbing loudly ]
whoa!

15:38.438 --> 15:43.041
Back it up.
Auntie sharon's gay, too?!

15:43.043 --> 15:44.342
Diane: Unbelievable.

15:45.945 --> 15:48.980
[ sighs ]
thanks a lot, bow.

15:48.982 --> 15:51.482
