to rock the boat.

15:51.484 --> 15:53.351
I told you to rock the boat,
dre,

15:53.353 --> 15:55.053
Not steer it
into an iceberg.

15:55.055 --> 15:56.120
Mm-hmm.

15:56.122 --> 15:58.289
Yo, bro!
Are you out your mind?

15:58.291 --> 16:00.458
