to out me to mom?

16:00.460 --> 16:02.660
Rhonda, I saw this
playing out differently.

16:02.662 --> 16:04.529
Look, I saw myself
as the hero,

16:04.531 --> 16:05.697
You know, cheers,
ticker tape,

16:05.699 --> 16:10.535
[ sighs ] okay. You're right.
I shouldn't have said anything.

16:10.537 --> 16:13.638
You can't put the toothpaste
back in the tube.

16:13.640 --> 16:17.709
[ sighs ]
sharon and I are
leaving...Soon.

16:17.711 --> 16:20.478
