a little bit of car trouble.

16:20.480 --> 16:22.513
[ sighs heavily ]

16:22.515 --> 16:23.514
[ dog barking in distance ]

16:23.516 --> 16:25.650
Mom?

16:25.652 --> 16:29.253
Mom, look.

16:29.255 --> 16:32.657
