I'm talking about --

16:46.573 --> 16:49.173
Mom, it's your and rhonda's
decision

16:49.175 --> 16:51.609
Whether you wanna talk
about it or not.

16:51.611 --> 16:55.046
If it works out for you guys
not to talk about it,

16:55.048 --> 16:56.514
Then that's just fine.

16:56.516 --> 16:58.349
[ whispers ]
thank you, baby.

16:58.351 --> 17:00.318
