on her.

17:19.639 --> 17:21.472
[ prays in tongues ]

17:21.474 --> 17:23.608
Of course,
that's mostly women.

17:23.610 --> 17:25.443
That could do more harm
than good.

17:25.445 --> 17:27.812
Mom! It's not a phase.
All right?
Hmm.

17:27.814 --> 17:30.515
Rhonda is who she is,

17:30.517 --> 17:33.518
And I'm not asking you to change
how you vote or how you feel!

17:33.520 --> 17:35.653
But this is your daughter.
Mnh-mnh!

17:35.655 --> 17:37.522
My sister.
Mnh-mnh!

17:37.524 --> 17:41.059
